ent-STWeaponRifleStalkerAK105SwampThing = AK-105 "Swamp Thing"
    .desc = The AK-105 is a compact Kalashnikov assault rifle from the "hundredth series." Designed for the 5.45x39mm cartridge, it is used by the Russian military and law enforcement agencies. This rifle is modified to meet the needs of special operatives throughout the Zone.
